Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開晚會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 彼得 快點 快點來看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是燈籠 好多燈籠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊 好像是白天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來的正是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請奏迎賓的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家請入座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們過去吧 爺爺\N恩
